<paragraph id="F90A36AA2506956EFF6EB366FA3E85CB" blockId="5.[151,1436,1898,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
There has long been confusion with regard to the presence of this species in Nova 
<collectingCountry id="81A2763A2506956EFB3CB366FB43859B" box="[1172,1249,1898,1924]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Scotia</collectingCountry>
. It was listed as occurring in Nova 
<collectingCountry id="81A2763A2506956EFEDCB39EFE1F85B3" box="[372,445,1938,1964]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Scotia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFE42B39EFD1385B3" author="Bousquet" box="[490,689,1938,1964]" pageId="5" pageNumber="33" refString="Bousquet, Y. (1991) Family Carabidae: ground beetles. In Bousquet, Y. (Ed.). Checklist of Beetles of Canada and Alaska. Agriculture Canada Publication 1861 / E. Ottawa, Ontario. pp. 8 - 60" type="journal article" year="1991">
Bousquet (
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFDC2B39EFD0B85B3" box="[618,681,1938,1964]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1991.0">1991</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFD16B39EFB8B85B3" author="Bousquet" box="[702,1065,1938,1964]" pageId="5" pageNumber="33" refString="Bousquet, Y. &amp; Larochelle, A. (1993) Catalogue of the Geadephaga (Coleoptera: Trachypachidae, Rhysodidae, Carabidae including Cicindelini) of America north of Mexico. Memoirs of the Entomological Society of Canada, 167, 1 - 397." type="journal article" year="1993">
Bousquet &amp; Larochelle (
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFC49B39EFB8285B3" box="[993,1056,1938,1964]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1993.0">1993</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFB9DB39EFAE485B3" author="Leonard" box="[1077,1350,1938,1964]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" refString="Leonard, J. G. &amp; Bell, R. T. (1999) Northeastern tiger beetles: a field guide to tiger beetles of New England and eastern Canada. CRC Press, Boca Raton, Florida. 176 pp." type="book" year="1999">
Leonard &amp; Bell (
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFB56B39EFA9F85B3" box="[1278,1341,1938,1964]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1999.0">1999</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFAFAB39EFF4A85CB" author="Acorn" pageId="5" pageNumber="33" refString="Acorn, J. (2001) Tiger beetles of Alberta: killers on the clay, stalkers on the sand. University of Alberta Press, Edmonton, Alberta. 120 pp." type="book" year="2001">
Acorn (
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFF37B3B6FF7C85CB" box="[159,222,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="2001.0">2001</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFF5FB3B6FD9E85CB" author="Goulet" box="[247,572,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" refString="Goulet, H. &amp; Bousquet, Y. (2004) The ground beetles of Canada. Available from: http: // digir. agr. gc. ca / spp _ pages / carabids / phps / index _ e. php (accessed 10 February 2007)." type="journal article" year="2004">
Goulet &amp; Bousquet (
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFE5CB3B6FD9685CB" box="[500,564,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="2004.0">2004</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFD29B3B6FC2385CB" box="[641,897,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="35" refString="Pearson, D. L., Knisley, C. B., &amp; Kazilek, C. J. (2006) A field guide to the tiger beetles of the United States and Canada. Oxford University Press, New York, NY. 227 pp." type="book">
Pearson 
<emphasis id="CBC1EAB82506956EFD40B3B7FC8485CB" box="[744,806,1979,2004]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFC91B3B6FCDB85CB" box="[825,889,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="2006.0">2006</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, but not by 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFBB0B3B6FB1985CB" author="Wallis" box="[1048,1211,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="36" refString="Wallis, J. B. (1961) The Cicindelidae of Canada. University of Toronto Press, Toronto, Ontario. 74 pp." type="book" year="1961">
<collectingCountry id="81A2763A2506956EFBB0B3B6FBC085CB" box="[1048,1122,1978,2004]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Wallis</collectingCountry>
(
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFBDEB3B6FB1185CB" box="[1142,1203,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1961.0">1961</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
or 
<bibRefCitation id="9D244B5B2506956EFB41B3B6FA3A85CB" author="Freitag" box="[1257,1432,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="34" refString="Freitag, R. (1999) Catalogue of the tiger beetles of Canada and the United States. NRC Research Press, Ottawa, Ontario. 192 pp." type="book" year="1999">
Freitag (
<number id="4F7D248D2506956EFAE7B3B6FA2D85CB" box="[1359,1423,1978,2004]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="1999.0">1999</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
